verseObjects.content: + \ft Some versions add, \fqa and the Lord Jesus Christ \fqa* .
+ \ft Some versions read, \fqa on your behalf \fqa* .
+ \ft Some versions read, \fqa who has made us able to have a share \fqa* .
+ \ft Some versions read, \fqa in whom we have redemption through his blood, the forgiveness of sins \fqa* .
